JOHANNESBURG – While Kwaito musician Sipho' Brickz' Ndlovu was being sentenced, it was the animated isiZulu interpreter, Sizakele Mhlongo, who stole the show. Mhlongo’s dramatic interpretation was the talk of the town on social media.    Brickz was sentenced to 15 years in prison for raping a teenage relative in 2013.  Watch the video in the gallery above. eNCA